<Rewrite PAsource="" >faced. </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >She said: </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >"There were only two women allowed on the unit - one in each of two teams - and I had to wait for one to leave before I could join. </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >On the </Verbatim>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >TSG </Verbatim>
