<New PAsource="" >like </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >furniture, </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >a token women. They had to have a black, so I was the </New>
<New PAsource="" >token black </New>
<New PAsource="" >- so they got </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >two for the price of one. </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >If they </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >saw a white and a black together, </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >it would be 'There goes </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >a salt and pepper team'. </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >They would use comments like BIF, </New>
<New PAsource="" >which meant 'black, ignorant f***er' </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >and </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >'groid'. which was </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >short for </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >negroid. </New>
<New PAsource="" >It was always going on."
</New>

