<New PAsource="" >WPC </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >said she </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >also faced a barrage of sex jibes. </Rewrite>
<New PAsource="" >She told </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >Horseferry Road Court: </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >"When I left the unit I needed a lot of counselling. It affected my marriage and I am now divorced. But at some point in your life you have got to stand up to these people. "
</New>

