<Verbatim PAsource="" >Hendricks </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >went on: </Rewrite>
<New PAsource="" >When I walked in he said, 'Watch out, here's </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >Stevie Lawrence Two'.</Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >
</New>

<New PAsource="" >I felt degraded. Here was an officer who was a skipper, yet he had still got the front to talk to me as if he was some bully out on the street. This guy had been bullying me for years. He is a copper with a responsible job who is supposed </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >to protect people like me. </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >I asked him to apologise three or four times but he just told me to f*** off.

He had a snooker cue which he lifted and he looked very angry. I thought he was going to hit me so I punched him, catching him by the jaw. Another officer grabbed me by both arms and pinned me against the snooker table. I was terrified. Mark Workman came back towards me and I thought he was going to assault me again so I kicked out. I only punched him once and kicked out at him once in self-defence.

They are two big six-foot guys end I am only five foot seven. Once I kicked him I got free and ran out.</New>

<New PAsource="" ></New>

